{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "彩排日", "storyInfo": "老演員道爾頓的死被製片人格蕾塔強硬地判定為意外，製片統籌謝莉卻認定這與五年前的某件舊事有關。弄假成真的“殺人”讓盧西恩回憶起過去劇團長為年幼的自己上的一課。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g3_filmset", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老道爾頓的死，是個意外——這就是結論。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫療組已經收殮他的遺體，調度短駁運輸車送回藍卡塢主城，並向警方報備事故詳情。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉也已經重新檢查了其他剩下的道具，排除了所有隱患。大家稍微休息一下，今天下午劇組就重啟拍攝。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼快？", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼問題嗎？", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "膠卷可以更換，攝影機壞了還有備用的，但這是死了一個人啊，我們才剛剛擦乾地面的血跡，就要……", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼道爾頓明明是去找道具，最後卻找到了一把開鋒的真刀？", "name": "工作人員B"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底是誰哄騙酒醉的演員自己去找遺失的道具？還是說，其實是有人故意把它塞到了道爾頓的手裡？", "name": "工作人員B"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哄騙？故、故意塞？", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道爾頓除了愛喝酒容易誤事，和劇組的大家也沒什麼私仇，誰會這樣做？", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且那把刀的形制很普通，劇組的廚房、街上的商店，甚至我們自己的房間，到處都有差不多的……", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得只是有人無心跟道爾頓提了一下，他就自己……", "name": "工作人員A"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，疑點很多，不是嗎？", "name": "工作人員B"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你只能自己去問道爾頓了，“偵探”小姐。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1845_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1847_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "工作人員B"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道大部分的人，包括我，仍沉浸在失去同伴的衝擊中，但現在有個最重要的問題擺在眼前——", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拍攝已臨近尾聲。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都知道藍卡塢專用於拍攝的移動地塊跟移動城市不同。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然同樣受到中心控制塔的管控，但部分調配權限會直接分享給劇組，我們就是受益於此才能將移動地塊開出藍卡塢主城區。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "租賃合約到期之後，攝影棚會陸續關閉，地塊將自動返航。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，更多操作空間也等於更高的維護成本。根據我簽署的合約，如果要臨時延長租賃合約，就需要支付一大筆違約金——", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而它會直接分攤到每一個人的薪資單上。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為製片人，我需要衡量全體成員的得失，確保我們的劇組能夠正常運轉。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我同意。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "身為主角兼投資人，我也同意。", "name": "米蘭妮"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，這位“偵探”小姐倒是提醒我了，有些責任確實需要追究。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道具組長？", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我在。", "name": "道具組長"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "管理道具，這是你的本職工作，很顯然，你有嚴重的過失。甚至，整個拍攝過程中，你手下的實習生都比你更早就位。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱、抱歉，格蕾塔女士。", "name": "道具組長"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，抱歉沒有任何意義。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即日開除出組。趁我們的移動地塊還沒開出主城區多遠，你可以儘早物色新的工作……別再說什麼了，你應該清楚，我已經足夠仁慈。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "道具組接下來的工作……我希望交由莫伊拉負責。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我……？", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你不願意，也可以選擇跟你的組長一起離開劇組，當然我相信你不會做那種愚蠢的決定。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，斯蒂芬，你需要把握時間了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "《杜邦夫人之死》的結局還差一口氣，這是我們的共識。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照原計劃，你應該在上週交出那幾場戲的定稿。顯然，拍攝進度馬上就要追上你的修改速度。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還要身兼導演工作，你知道我們這個劇組其實很令人操心……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#7$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是沒有好的靈感？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#4$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的原創劇本，這是你最珍愛的故事，給它一個最好的結局吧，親愛的。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是我最在意的事情。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "杜邦夫人在經歷一連串的變故後，到底是被哪個洛克菲勒殺死？在什麼場景裡？以什麼姿勢？她死前說了什麼？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這決定了這部電影的水準。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她怎麼在戲裡好看地死，決定了我怎麼在藍卡塢漂亮地重生……", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我把我全部的身家都投入這部戲了，兩位。", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#1$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……神會來找我的。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "米蘭妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1830_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，文學評論裡有一種說法，說所謂的“靈感”，是指神明直接附身在作者身上，代替他寫下新生與死亡，毀滅與希望……", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，請放心，我會完成這個故事。", "name": "斯蒂芬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1835_1#1$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那好，散會，去做準備吧。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士！格蕾塔女士！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有很重要的事要找你談——", "name": "謝莉"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉，我知道你要說什麼，但不是現在。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得先去看看盧西恩，他才剛來劇組，第一次參與電影拍攝就經歷了這麼嚴重的意外……", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得確保他不會落荒而逃。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於你，無論你聯想到了什麼……忘了它，你想多了。", "name": "格蕾塔"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "謝莉"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……我來負責整個道具組？", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恭喜你啊，莫麗！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然道爾頓剛過世不久——願他安息，但我真的為你高興。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在藍卡塢的工作時間比你久多了，但到現在也還只是個畫布景的，晉升的機會真的很難得。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是因為蒂比總是喜歡把自己的主張加入背景，所以你們美術組的組長不敢讓你負責更多。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我只是從開拓區來藍卡塢謀生的手工愛好者，真的能……", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士說你可以，你就可以！她的眼光一向很準。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且你的姐姐也會很高興的，你不是受到她的影響才來藍卡塢的嗎？快點告訴她你現在已經是獨當一面的道具組長啦！", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等晚上再跟她通話吧。我不能辜負格蕾塔女士的信任，得把工作做好才行。", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦~不錯嘛，現在已經開始有組長的樣子了哦？說不定再過兩天連找你看恐怖片你都不會賞臉啦。", "name": "蒂比"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蒂比！", "name": "莫伊拉"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g1_setting_lobby", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，別在我眼前晃來晃去了，謝莉！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "分鏡表確認了三次，設備檢查了五次。我向製片人女士發過毒誓，不會再弄丟一台攝影機了，可以別盯著我了嗎！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）你說……真的是這樣嗎？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？什麼？大聲一點。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#6$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說道爾頓的死真的是意外嗎？你就不覺得有什麼不對勁的地方？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關我什麼事。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個傢伙整天把自己泡在酒桶裡，這兩個月不知道害我晚下班幾次，現在終於安靜了。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他五年前還不是這樣。", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廢話，那時候他還在格蕾塔和斯蒂芬的片子裡擔任主角，正值事業巔峰，那個時候我們不是也在嗎？", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是最不對勁的！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開籌備會的時候，我在工作人員名單裡看到了很多眼熟的名字，實際見到你們的面孔之後更加害怕，就好像——", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就好像真的回到了五年前，再一次目睹了那名小演員的死？", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不覺得這兩起事故……很像嗎？", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#6$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡像了？一個是墜亡，一個是道具刀弄錯了。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉，你又開始杞人憂天了。", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#9$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很理智……哦……我全都搞清楚了！道爾頓不就是當時那起事故的主要責任人嗎！", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#3$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他遭到報應了……有人來找他了……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "暫停！別再抓你的手臂也別再胡思亂想了。我早就跟你說過——多看醫生，遠離劇組！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#4$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是拍爛片謀生的普通人，沒人把我們當回事。謝莉？謝莉，我說的話你聽到了沒有！", "name": "阿布納"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1843_1#8$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽到了……我聽到了……有什麼要來了，要來找我們了……", "name": "謝莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1836_1#4$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_RL_castlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你需要在腦海中構想下刀的位置和角度。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "右腹下方是臟器的間隙，血管分布密集但不致命。你可以藉他人之血抒情，為之後的高潮段落埋下伏筆。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者將刀尖上移，刺穿胸腔。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "脆弱的肺葉沒有任何抵抗能力，對方會慢慢溺死在自己的血和你慷慨激昂的獨白之中。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "舉起你的匕首，孩子。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想想我們已經排演過的段落，你一直表現得很好，只差這最後一步。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刺下去！讓刀尖體會攪動內臟、割斷血管的觸感，讓它聆聽心跳的聲音！", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你害怕了？", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……平庸的孩子。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.6}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他並非膽怯，只是心有不解。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長，他到現在還不願練習刺殺，握住匕首後就再沒說過話了。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.6, "focus": "l", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "200,0"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "辛苦你了，去準備明天的演出吧。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我來指導這個孩子。", "name": "劇團長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您親自……我明白了。", "name": "“白英花”"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1841_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子，匕首重嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……重。", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你知道，它的重量並不來自金屬和裝飾，而是源自你的心，對嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頭髮遮住了男孩的眉眼，他沉默著點頭。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“白英花”未能料到你領悟得如此之快，你在等她解惑，而她做不到。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽我說，孩子……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長握住了盧西恩的小手，他的微笑是溫柔的，手上的力道卻強硬，不容拒絕。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩覺得自己僵硬的手指在慢慢放鬆。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忘掉“白英花”試圖教你的那些技巧，你不需要模仿某一種握刀姿勢或是刺殺方法。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有不染血的匕首、不被擊發的弩，握緊它們就好。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它們不是道具，它們會教會你該渴望什麼。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，讓它們牽引你的行動，別懷疑，哪怕它指向的對象是你沒有想過的人——親友、摯愛，甚至自己……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或者，此刻站在你面前的我。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……你？", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別猶豫，揮下去。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "試試看嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "試試看。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（搖頭）", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "試試看。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你，那我……", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們在扮演什麼？", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然已經遺忘了技巧，那角色和台詞也暫且忘記吧，它們只是戲劇的載體，而非戲劇本身。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩終於握緊了刀，劇團長放開了他的手，半跪在他身前，讓兩人保持差不多的高度。"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是，我們離得太近太近了……", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很怕傷害到我嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，孩子。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連這種情緒也一併遺忘吧。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信我，你會沉浸，你會觸碰到戲劇的美。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看著劇團長，盧西恩萌生出強烈的疑惑——這是否是自己第一次見到他？"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他理解不了對方說的所有話，他甚至懷疑這個男性菲林其實並不存在。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩可以確定的是，自己的心臟在跳動。"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，心跳不會作假，心跳會給他答案。"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他要以什麼方式去詢問？"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長微笑著，他在無聲地鼓勵自己。"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "答案顯而易見。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩毫不猶豫地揮刀——"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$knifegore"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_slash_02_s", "x": 170.0, "roy": 89.0, "roz": 150.0, "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "感受到了嗎？", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩的手在顫抖，一擊之後，他的力氣差點用盡，險些握不住刀柄。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長沒有移動分毫，甚至連表情都沒有變化。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但盧西恩很確信刀刃劃開了對方的身體，他聽到了聲音……他感受到了本不屬於他的疼痛——強烈的、肆意的疼痛。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來到劇團後，他一直沉默，但此刻，那疼痛讓他突然想要歌唱。"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你的第一課，孩子——所有的故事最終都只會剩下某種情緒，或者……", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "劇團長停頓了一下，盧西恩投去追問的目光，於是他對上了那對金色的瞳孔。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "某段密不可分的關係。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "小盧西恩"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1829_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是天生的演員，你應該成為我的學生。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "考慮好之後，來找我……盧西恩，我永遠不會成為你的阻礙。", "name": "劇團長"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 2.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g10_dormitory", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩低頭看向自己的雙手。"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "手套上的血跡早已清洗乾淨，但他依然無法忘記從道爾頓手中奪過刀時的感覺。"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉醉、忘我。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如他的師長第一次教他使用匕首時湧出的複雜感受。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "忘記純熟的刺殺技巧，僅用濃烈的情緒點燃自我，只剩下兩個靈魂彼此撕咬。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將生命收束於亦真亦假的小刀，賜予對方完美的終局——"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死亡。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩。", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#6$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的臉色有點差……你還好嗎？", "name": "格蕾塔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1834_1#4$1"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}